<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得復活蛋的顏色　<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該是有什麼意義的，<10_4 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我稍微思考了一下，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />紅色是熱情如火的愛，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />藍色是包圍著我們的宇宙，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />白色是與生俱來的純潔。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我不知道正確答案，<delay20 />
不過那小小的畫布裡，<delay20 />
應該包含了某個人的祈禱呢。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才在廣場上
跟<colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />打招呼時，<delay20 />嚇了他一跳呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來他很不習慣別人站在他背後。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你也想跟他打招呼，<delay20 />
記得不要站在他背後喔。<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />話說回來，那個拉鍊是<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節，顧名思義，<delay20 />
就是有東西復活的意思喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我由衷地希望<delay20 />不管是什麼節日，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家都能有個美好的開始……</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是聽<colour id="3" />陸德里<colour id="65535" />說的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個時期<delay20 />使用哩數旅行券旅行的話，<delay20 />
在前往的那座島上，岩石邊常常都會有蛋喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是只有復活節時期<delay20 />
才能看到的風景呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />差不多到復活節的時候，<delay20 />
這座島就會被施展魔法。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說，敲擊椰子樹後，<delay20 />
掉下來的不是椰子，<delay20 />
而是長得不可思議的蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這類的魔法。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />這就是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Easter Magic啊！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節就快到了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到復活節<tag a="110" b="0" />
就會想起彩色的蛋呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道<delay20 />我能不能也畫出那樣的圖案呢？<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不知道怎樣畫才對<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我會畫上跟我的愛等量的愛心喔。</message>
